Package: GroupCONSORT
Title: Group-Stratified CONSORT Flowcharts for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A pipe-friendly toolkit for tracking patient attrition through
    inclusion and exclusion criteria and producing publication-quality CONSORT
    flowcharts stratified by site or country group. Flowchart layout adapts
    automatically to the number of steps, groups, and text length.
